org.mixare.data.convert

Interface DataProcessor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MixareDataProcessor, OsmDataProcessor, PanoramioDataProcessor, RemoteDataHandler, TwitterDataProcessor, WikiDataProcessor

    public interface DataProcessor
    A data processor interface, Classes that are implemented by this interface are responsible for converting raw data into markers. This class also contains 2 abstract methods, those methods can be implemented by the interface and they describe the conditions that are needed for the processor to be activated
    Author:
    A. Egal
